div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Enhance your living room's interior design with our solutions!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20124603\/enhance-your-living-rooms-interior-design-with-our-solutions.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go Clutter Free With A U Shaped Living Room Sofa Set<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Fans of the pristine lines and elegance of the Scandinavian aesthetic will appreciate paring back the living room aesthetic. Make a statement using a large sectional such as a U-shaped living room sofa set. Keep other furniture and d\u00e9cor elements to a minimum letting the sofa set be the centre of attention in your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235837\/u-shaped-living-room-sofa-sets.jpg\" alt=\"Latest u shaped white sofa for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4119\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235837\/u-shaped-living-room-sofa-sets.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235837\/u-shaped-living-room-sofa-sets-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235837\/u-shaped-living-room-sofa-sets-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235837\/u-shaped-living-room-sofa-sets-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A white u shaped sofa set with complementary modern arm chairs stands out in a minimalist living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Someplace To Stretch and Binge Watch<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have lots of family or guests to entertain? Love huddling together to catch the latest on TV? Bring in a long and narrow L-shaped sofa and face it pointing towards your television. Look for practical colours like darker hues of brown and blue that wear well and are sturdy. Get sofa throws on and bring out the popcorn to get ready to party!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235841\/l-shaped-sofa-for-modern-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Latest l shaped sofa designs for small living room, it works like a charm in narrow living room\" class=\"wp-image-4120\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235841\/l-shaped-sofa-for-modern-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235841\/l-shaped-sofa-for-modern-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235841\/l-shaped-sofa-for-modern-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235841\/l-shaped-sofa-for-modern-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>The long L-shaped sofa works like a charm in this narrow living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Evening Attire for Your Modern Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuxedos are not just formal attire for men, they are a style of living room sofa that are known for their clean lines and boxy shape. Get one for your living room if you like this style \u2013 a straight back with arms at the same height as the back. A tuxedo style sofa can add class to any living room. You can go big or small depending on your living room\u2019s dimensions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235845\/grey-sofa-sets-modern-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Grey sofa sets can add class look to your modern living room, it is a sofa set designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4121\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235845\/grey-sofa-sets-modern-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235845\/grey-sofa-sets-modern-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235845\/grey-sofa-sets-modern-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235845\/grey-sofa-sets-modern-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A handsome Tuxedo style sofa in grey that makes for a fuss free look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make A Colourful Statement In A Plain Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Add no end of pizzazz to a plain living room by choosing a sofa set in an unexpected colour. Given that sofas comprise such a large proportion of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-furniture-design-ideas\/\">furniture in the living room<\/a>, their design style and colour can be a game changer for the overall look. So, go ahead and pick a contrasting or bold colour for your living room sofa set and jazz up your space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235850\/contrasting-bold-colour-for-living-room-sofa-set.jpg\" alt=\"Pick a contrasting or bold colour for your latest sofa set designs for living room, these are the sofa designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4122\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235850\/contrasting-bold-colour-for-living-room-sofa-set.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235850\/contrasting-bold-colour-for-living-room-sofa-set-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235850\/contrasting-bold-colour-for-living-room-sofa-set-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235850\/contrasting-bold-colour-for-living-room-sofa-set-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A burst of blue makes the otherwise sombre living room come alive<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Mid-Century Wooden Sofa Set Design For Small Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make a small living room look spacious and airy by introducing a sofa set designed in the mid-century style. The mid-century style was known for its high elevated sofas with clean lines and simple silhouettes. Combine a 2+1+1 arrangement or go for a 2+1 arrangement based on the living room space available.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235854\/wooden-sofa-set-designs-for-small-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden sofa design for living room with a green and yellow mid-century sofa\" class=\"wp-image-4123\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235854\/wooden-sofa-set-designs-for-small-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235854\/wooden-sofa-set-designs-for-small-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235854\/wooden-sofa-set-designs-for-small-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235854\/wooden-sofa-set-designs-for-small-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A green and yellow mid-century sofa set that lightens and brightens a living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go Sophisticated With A Leather Sofa Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If the sophisticated and deeply luxurious look is your style, go with leather. Leather sofas, especially in handsome dark colours such as black and brown add a sense of mystery to the room. While leather has been traditionally used for sofas, this versatile material seamlessly lends itself to a modern and contemporary style as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235858\/leather-sofa-design-for-modern-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Leather sofa design for living room interiors with a brown leather chesterfield fits\" class=\"wp-image-4124\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235858\/leather-sofa-design-for-modern-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235858\/leather-sofa-design-for-modern-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235858\/leather-sofa-design-for-modern-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235858\/leather-sofa-design-for-modern-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A brown leather Chesterfield fits right into rich and modern interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lay Out Squares With A Sectional<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Experiment with the number of pieces in a sectional to determine the right fit for you.&nbsp; While many sectionals have two pieces like a sofa and a loveseat, consider the combination that has two &#8211; one armed sofas and a corner chair in the middle. This style <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-partition-design-ideas\/\">partitions your living room<\/a> into zones results in a pleasing sense of symmetry and style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235902\/square-sofa-sets-with-armed-sofas-corner-chair-living-area.jpg\" alt=\"Latest sofa designs for living room with square sofa sets with one armed sofas in the middle for your living area\" class=\"wp-image-4125\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235902\/square-sofa-sets-with-armed-sofas-corner-chair-living-area.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235902\/square-sofa-sets-with-armed-sofas-corner-chair-living-area-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235902\/square-sofa-sets-with-armed-sofas-corner-chair-living-area-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235902\/square-sofa-sets-with-armed-sofas-corner-chair-living-area-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A spacious square sectional that provides plenty of seating<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bit Of Japan In Your Living Room Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The futon is inspired by Japanese bedding and is another superb sofa for a small living rooms. A futon can typically be configured in several ways \u2013 to be a couch, recliner or even a flatbed. Get a single seater for tight spaces or when combining it with other sofa pieces. You can also get a double futon for a larger space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235906\/futon-japanese-bedding-sofa-for-small-living-rooms.jpg\" alt=\"Futon japanese bedding sofa design for small modern living rooms be configured with a couch for sofa designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4127\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235906\/futon-japanese-bedding-sofa-for-small-living-rooms.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235906\/futon-japanese-bedding-sofa-for-small-living-rooms-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235906\/futon-japanese-bedding-sofa-for-small-living-rooms-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235906\/futon-japanese-bedding-sofa-for-small-living-rooms-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>The casual comfort of this green futon is ideal for this bright living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Rattan Sofa That Is Perfect For Two<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rattan is a lightweight, natural and durable material. Sofas made of rattan are visually appealing while bringing a sense of lightness thus making them ideal for sofa set designs for small living rooms. Limit the number of seats to further open a cramped space up.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235910\/rattan-lightweight-sofa-set-designs-small-living-rooms.jpg\" alt=\"Rattan lightweight sofa set designs made for cosying up in your small living room for sofa designs\" class=\"wp-image-4128\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235910\/rattan-lightweight-sofa-set-designs-small-living-rooms.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235910\/rattan-lightweight-sofa-set-designs-small-living-rooms-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235910\/rattan-lightweight-sofa-set-designs-small-living-rooms-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235910\/rattan-lightweight-sofa-set-designs-small-living-rooms-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A rattan loveseat made for cosying up in your living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Put Your Feet Up During the Day<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Get a daybed to solve studio or small apartment woes. This sofa for a small room is a couch by day and a bed by night making it multi-purpose. These typically do not have back support but there are things you can do to make it more comfortable in its sofa avatar. Throw on some plump cushions and place it against a wall for increased cosiness.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235913\/daybed-living-room-sofa-couch-cum-bed.jpg\" alt=\"Daybed for a small living room is a couch by day and a bed by night making it multi-purpose for sofa designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4129\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235913\/daybed-living-room-sofa-couch-cum-bed.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235913\/daybed-living-room-sofa-couch-cum-bed-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235913\/daybed-living-room-sofa-couch-cum-bed-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235913\/daybed-living-room-sofa-couch-cum-bed-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>An elegant daybed in cream is perfect for rich marble and wooden interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Avail 20% extra space with our space saving interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/12180805\/avail-20-percent-extra-space-with-our-space-saving-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Simple Sofa Set Design For Small Living Rooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you are looking to design small living rooms, sometimes the answer lies in keeping it simple. Opt for an L shaped sofa set but keep it compact and fuss free. Avoid fancy details and rich patterns which are more suitable for large spaces. Pick a neutral colour palette and add hints of texture. Work with the contours of the space to correctly position your sofa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235917\/simple-sofa-design-for-small-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Simple sofa set design for small living rooms with a compact l-shaped sofa is neatly tucked in the corner for sofa designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4130\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235917\/simple-sofa-design-for-small-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235917\/simple-sofa-design-for-small-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235917\/simple-sofa-design-for-small-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235917\/simple-sofa-design-for-small-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A compact L-shaped sofa is neatly tucked in the corner in a small living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bring A Touch Of The Boudoir To Your Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The chaise lounge has a rich history. From being synonymous with a psychotherapist\u2019s couch to being a classic item redolent of stylish boudoirs, this long reclining sofa has seen it all. Put into your living room as a sofa piece to bring that whiff of style and class.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235921\/long-reclining-sofa-in-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Long reclining sofa for living room, this sofa piece to bring that whiff of style and class for sofa designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4131\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235921\/long-reclining-sofa-in-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235921\/long-reclining-sofa-in-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235921\/long-reclining-sofa-in-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235921\/long-reclining-sofa-in-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Recline in stylish class with a traditional chaise lounge<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go Vintage With The Camelback<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The camelback sofa design is a traditional one, characterised by a camel\u2019s hump in the centre of the backrest. Exposed wooden legs and exposed wood on top of back and arms makes the camelback a great choice for those looking for a traditional sofa with fabulous upholstery. Modern day camelback sofas have one, two or even three humps.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235925\/classical-camelback-sofa-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Camelback sofa design is a visually stunning for small living room for sofa designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-4132\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235925\/classical-camelback-sofa-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235925\/classical-camelback-sofa-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235925\/classical-camelback-sofa-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235925\/classical-camelback-sofa-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>A visually stunning and classical Camelback sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You have no dearth of choices when it comes to sofas for your living room. Begin by determining the size of sofa your space can afford, the number and arrangement of seats, the style and colour palette. Voila! You have a sofa that is perfect for your modern living room \u2013 one which encourages you to put your feet up and let your hair down.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Sofa Set Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Can I mix and match different sofa designs in my living room?<\/strong><br>Yes, you can absolutely mix and match different sofa designs in your living room. But it is important that they are relatively similar in size to avoid one sofa overpowering the others. Make sure to choose complementary or coordinating colors as it can help tie the different designs together.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do I choose the right fabric for my sofa design?<\/strong><br>It depends on the look you aim to create and how the sofa will be used. Smooth fabrics like leather or silk can create a sleek and sophisticated look, while textured fabrics like velvet or tweed can add depth and visual interest. If you have children or pets or if the sofa will be heavily used, opt for a durable fabric such as microfiber, leather, or tightly woven synthetic blends. These are relatively easy to wipe clean as compared to other fabrics like velvet and linen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Are leather sofas a good option for a living room?<\/strong><br>Yes. Leather is a classic and timeless option for living room sofas. Leather sofas are durable, easy to clean, and give a sophisticated look. Moreover, leather comes in different finishes and price points. So you can easily buy one or get one customized within your budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Should I opt for a sectional or a traditional sofa design for my living room?<\/strong><br>Sectional sofas are always a better choice as compared to traditional sofas. Sectionals are a great choice for compact living rooms and open-concept spaces as they can effectively divide and define different areas. So whether you have a spacious living room or a compact one, a sectional can provide ample seating and create a cozy and inviting atmosphere.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">Latest Living Room Designs<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/small-living-room-decorating-ideas\/\">Small Living Room Decorating Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/modern-living-room-design-ideas\/\">10 Modern Living Room Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Dreamy Interiors That Spell 'WOW'<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our design experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class